{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778977643475,"sessionID":"ses_1ccbbf94effeJuWf8Ry3Dh7s3w","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"apply_patch","callID":"call_1KJpym3dUFsK7ZFxzHLLULtl","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"patchText":"*** Begin Patch\n*** Add File: ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+Added `GO:7770074 protein O-linked glycosylation via N-acetylglucosamine` as a child of `GO:0006493 protein O-linked glycosylation`, with the requested exact synonyms and PMID:35536957 as definition support.\n+\n+Changes committed in PR #<NN>.\n+\n*** Add File: PR_COMMENTS.md\n+# Summary\n+\n+Added a new biological process term:\n+\n+* `GO:7770074 protein O-linked glycosylation via N-acetylglucosamine`\n+\n+The term is placed under `GO:0006493 protein O-linked glycosylation` and includes the requested exact synonyms:\n+\n+* `protein O-linked GlcNAcylation`\n+* `protein O-linked-N-acetylglucosaminylation`\n+\n+# Rationale\n+\n+The issue requested a distinct BP term for O-GlcNAcylation so that Ogt, Eogt, and orthologs can be annotated more specifically than the generic parent `protein O-linked glycosylation`.\n+\n+The new term follows the existing local pattern used for sister terms such as `protein O-linked glycosylation via glucose`, `via galactose`, `via arabinose`, and `via xylose`: an asserted subclass of `GO:0006493`, a text definition describing the initiating O-linked sugar, and no logical definition. No specific DOSDP pattern was found for this branch, so no `intersection_of` axioms were added.\n+\n+PMID:35536957 was validated and supports the definition. The cached reference title is \"The O-GlcNAc Modification.\" It describes O-GlcNAc as modification of serine or threonine hydroxyl groups on proteins by O-linked beta-N-acetylglucosamine.\n+\n+# Validation\n+\n+* Pre-validation: `make travis_build` passed before edits.\n+* Post-edit validation: `make travis_build` passed after adding the term.\n+* Reference validation: `linkml-reference-validator validate text-file -r 'SUPPORT: (\\S+:\\S+) \"(.*)\"' -t 2 -R 1 RESEARCH.md` passed.\n+\n+# Checklist\n+\n+* PLAN: issue context analyzed; request was clear.\n+* PRE-VALIDATION: current ontology validated before edits.\n+* RESEARCH: `RESEARCH.md` created; PMID:35536957 validated.\n+* TERM-SEARCH: GO parent and sister terms searched in `src/ontology/go-edit.obo`.\n+* DESIGN-PATTERNS: `DESIGN_PATTERNS.md` created; existing GO precedent checked; no `intersection_of` added.\n+* EDITS: new term created in `terms/` and checked into `src/ontology/go-edit.obo` with `obo-checkin.pl`.\n+* RELATIONSHIPS: asserted `is_a: GO:0006493`; no over-specified logical definition.\n+* SPECIALIZED-EDITS: chemical-entity skill consulted because the request names N-acetylglucosamine; no CHEBI axiom was added.\n+* METADATA: term tracker item, `created_by`, and `creation_date` added for the new term.\n+* AUTOMATED-VALIDATION: post-edit `make travis_build` passed.\n+* REFERENCE-VALIDATION: PMID support text validated.\n+* CHANGES-COMMITTED: committed locally as `59d5ecd Add protein O-linked GlcNAc glycosylation term`.\n+\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\nA PR_COMMENTS.md","metadata":{"diff":"Index: /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/ISSUE_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,3 @@\n+Added `GO:7770074 protein O-linked glycosylation via N-acetylglucosamine` as a child of `GO:0006493 protein O-linked glycosylation`, with the requested exact synonyms and PMID:35536957 as definition support.\n+\n+Changes committed in PR #<NN>.\n\nIndex: /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md\n===================================================================\n--- /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md\n+++ /__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/PR_COMMENTS.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,39 @@\n+#